com.tguzik.tests

Enum Loader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Loader>
      • com.tguzik.tests.Loader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Loader>

    public enum Loader
extends Enum<Loader>
    Unit test utility that loads files. Primary use case is reading text files and using the contents as expected values in unit tests. This is placed in main sources (not test sources) to allow using this class in projects that depend on this library.

    Loaded files have their newline characters normalized to single '\n' character using Normalize.newLines(String). Loaded files are not trimmed - whitespace at the beginning and the end of the file will be preserved.

    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Tomasz Guzik
